public/hot 
public/hot 

# The public/storage entry must always be Laravel's symlink to
# storage/app/public (created by `php artisan storage:link`), never a
# real, committed directory — a real directory here silently breaks
# `storage:link` (it refuses to overwrite an existing path), which is
# why uploaded voice notes/avatars 404'd in production.
/public/storage
